{"kind":"notes","id":"nt/hwbqtkby","slide":2,"text":"0:20–0:50 — The line sees the stop. Energy sees a restart envelope. Quality sees incomplete process history. Logistics sees a truck at 06:30. One 24-kilometre order now has three truths: drums one to six remain outside the incident, drum seven is entirely on hold, and drum eight is not started and must be replanned. Restarting the line is not the same as recovering the operation."}
