{"kind":"notes","id":"nt/ofy9wn61","slide":3,"text":"0:50–1:20 — CableTwin is a local, read-only decision layer. Explainable ML retrieves comparable synthetic cases and shows distance, differences and out-of-distribution warning. The deterministic twin tests recovery futures across energy, process, material, people, quality and delivery. Hard rules reject impossible sequences. CableTwin never commands a PLC and never releases cable: Quality, the laboratory and accountable humans keep authority."}
