{"kind":"notes","id":"nt/jyx0ra1s","slide":4,"text":"1:20–1:50 — LIVE ONLY AFTER ACCEPT: Here is the same scenario in Jury mode. I inject the 58-minute outage: drum seven stays on hold and the system retrieves comparable cases. I reduce available restart power: no plan is feasible. I restore the operator-entered limit: staged Plan C returns under visible assumptions. The laboratory gate remains closed. Same engine, same rules, faster replay—not a scripted shortcut. PRE-ACCEPT FALLBACK: describe this as the acceptance contract, not a live capability."}
