{"kind":"notes","id":"nt/m90b6t0r","slide":10,"text":"3:40–4:00 — Our ask is precise: select CableTwin and connect one Tunisian cable-plant design partner for a read-only shadow pilot. A power interruption lasts 58 minutes; industrial uncertainty can last for hours. CableTwin retrieves the past, compares futures, blocks the impossible—and leaves authorization to humans and the laboratory."}